NightViper watched the attack begin and he quickly transformed and 
slithered between the rocks hidden from sight. "Watch your pretty 
little tail there Commander."
********************************
Rave ducked and cawed. "Chrono, fire main guns."

"Unable to comply... system failure... Shields wil faill in... i... 
i... i.." The computer shut down and Rave cursed as the shields 
dropped. "Alright Pred heads... bring iAIEEEeeeeee!"

NightViper coiled around the smaller bot. "Ssso nice to meet you 
black birdie, but i am afraid you are oursss."

Rave reached for the bomb but remembered he'd placed in it the med-
lab. He quickly activated his com-link. "BOSS!"
